	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is it possible to add a a attribute table grid overlay option to the nametable viewer. That would make it easier/faster  to see which tiles are part of which attribute table entry. <br /><br />Or maybe add the attribute table address of the current part of the screen you are hovering over.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
